    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * BBchess</b>\n</p><p><b>BBchess</b>,<br />\na chess program by <a href=\"/Bernard_Brioit\" title=\"Bernard Brioit\">Bernard Brioit</a>. The engine part was written in <a href=\"/Pascal\" title=\"Pascal\">Pascal</a>, its own <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> written in <a href=\"/Delphi\" title=\"Delphi\">Delphi</a>. \nBBchess uses the <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a> <a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board representation</a> and performs an improved <a href=\"/MTD(f)\" title=\"MTD(f)\">MTD(f) search</a> on top of <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">iterative deepening</a> and applies <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null move pruning</a> with a <a href=\"/Depth_Reduction_R\" title=\"Depth Reduction R\">depth reduction</a> of 3 <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nIt uses two <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">transposition tables</a>, and supports the <a href=\"/Thompson%27s_Databases\" title=\"Thompson&#39;s Databases\">Thompson endgame databases</a> with three and four pieces <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Tournament_Play\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tournament Play</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Namesake\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Namesake</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tournament_Play\">Tournament Play</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=BBchess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Tournament Play\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>BBchess played all <a href=\"/French_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"French Computer Chess Championship\">French Computer Chess Championships</a> from <a href=\"/FCCC_1996\" title=\"FCCC 1996\">FCCC 1996</a> until its last occurence at the <a href=\"/FCCC_2004\" title=\"FCCC 2004\">FCCC 2004</a>, as well the <a href=\"/French_Programmers_Tournament\" title=\"French Programmers Tournament\">French Programmers Tournaments</a> from <a href=\"/Massy_2001\" title=\"Massy 2001\">Massy 2001</a> until <a href=\"/Massy_2006\" title=\"Massy 2006\">Massy 2006</a>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Namesake\">Namesake</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=BBchess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Namesake\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/BBChess_(SI)\" title=\"BBChess (SI)\">BBChess</a> by <a href=\"/Borko_Bo%C5%A1kovi%C4%87\" title=\"Borko Bošković\">Borko Bošković</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=BBchess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/BB\" title=\"BB\">BB</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bebe\" title=\"Bebe\">Bebe</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=BBchess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=32639&amp;start=1\">Re: ZChess getting much stronger...</a> by <a href=\"/Franck_Zibi\" title=\"Franck Zibi\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 10, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/ZChess\" title=\"ZChess\">ZChess</a>, <a href=\"/FCCC_2000\" title=\"FCCC 2000\">FCCC 2000</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=233358\">El Chinito and BBChess, information in English available ...</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 01, 2002&#160;» <a href=\"/Chinito\" title=\"Chinito\">Chinito</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=BBchess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.open-aurec.com/wbforum/viewtopic.php?f=18&amp;t=32639&amp;start=1\">Re: ZChess getting much stronger...</a> by <a href=\"/Franck_Zibi\" title=\"Franck Zibi\">Franck Zibi</a>, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Winboard Forum</a>, November 10, 2000</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessprogram.de/messages/19513.htm\">Interview with BBChess programmer Bernhard Brioit ...</a> (May 31th, 2002 Deutsch, Français, English) by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a> from the Schachwerkstatt Archives, September 4, 2006 (dead link)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260228221444\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 51/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 106/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6252-0!canonical and timestamp 20260228221444 and revision id 21234\n -->\n"
